description:
The show opens with a dedication to all kitchen beauticians. Papa John's founder uses N-word. Stormy Daniels gets arrested. Cardi B. has a new family member. Whitney Houston is at the center of controversy. Kylie Jenner is on the cover of Forbes. Are You Smarter Than Tommy? Carla's Reality Update is back. Sheryl Underwood stops by.
